<odoo>
    <template id="mode_paiement_custom" name="Mode Paiement">
         <t t-call="website.layout">
    <style>
            .title{
            text-align: left;
            font: normal normal bold 24px/29px Roboto;
            color: #000000;
            }
            .paragraph{
            font: normal normal normal 14px/24px Roboto;
            color: #000000;
            text-align: left;
            }
            .underline{
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-weight:normal;
            }
            span{
            font-weight: bold;
            }
            .bigtitle{
            font: normal normal bold 36px/29px Roboto;
            letter-spacing: 0px;
            color: #000000;
            text-align: center;
            }
            .greentitle{
            font: normal normal bold 14px/24px Roboto;
            letter-spacing: 0px;
            color: #91B508;
            }
            .s_faq_collapse .accordion .card .card-header.collapsed:before{
            float:right;
            }
            .s_faq_collapse .accordion .card .card-header:before {
            content: '\f107';
            float: right;
            }
            .s_faq_collapse .accordion .card .card-header.collapsed:before {
            content: '\f105';
            }
            .description{
            font: normal normal normal 11px/20px Poppins;
            color: #615C6E;
            }
            .bluep{
            text-decoration: underline;
            font: normal normal normal 11px/20px Poppins;
            color: #0088FF;
            }
            }
        </style>
    <div id="wrap" class="oe_structure oe_empty">
      <section class="s_title pt32 o_colored_level pb16 " data-vcss="001" data-snippet="s_title" data-name="Title">
        <div class="s_allow_columns container">
          <h1 class="bigtitle">Modes de paiements</h1>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="s_text_block o_colored_level" data-snippet="s_text_block" data-name="Text">
        <div class="container s_allow_columns">
          <h2 class="paragraph">
              Avec Pépin de pomme, la qualité et la sureté sont les maîtres-mots, tant au niveau des articles proposés et des services qu’au niveau des paiements. Afin de donner satisfaction à tous les clients qui peuvent avoir chacun le mode de paiement qui les convient, Pépin de pomme propose 4 modes de paiement pour <b>vos achats en ligne 100% sécurisé.</b>
          </h2>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="container fluid mb64 o_colored_level">

            <!-- foreach -->
            <t t-foreach="paiements" t-as="paiement">
                  <div class="card mb-2">
            <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-3">
              <div class="card-body o_payment_acquirer_select text-center text-md-left pb-0">
                  <t t-foreach="paiement.payment_icon_ids" t-as="icon">
                      <img class="img-fluid o_we_custom_image" t-attf-src="data:image/*;base64,{{icon.image}}"
  t-att-alt="icon.name"/>
                  </t>
               </div>
            </div>
                 <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
              <div class="card-body o_payment_acquirer_select text-center text-md-left">
                <label class="mb-0">
                  <span class="payment_option_name" t-field="paiement.name">

                                             </span>
                </label>
                <p class="description" t-field="paiement.description">

                                    </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            </div>
                  </div>
            </t>


            <!-- end foreach-->






      </section>
      <section class="s_icon_block_2 pb32 o_colored_level pt0" style="border-top: solid 1px #CFCFD1" data-snippet="s_icon_block_2" data-name="Icon Block - 2">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 py-3 text-center o_colored_level col-lg-4">
              <h5 class="mt-3">
                <img class="img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="/pepindepomme_custom_website/static/src/img/home/delivery.png" alt="" loading="lazy" data-original-id="596" data-original-src="data:image/png;base64," data-mimetype="image/png"/>
                <font style="font: normal normal bold 22px/27px Roboto; color: #000000;">&amp;nbsp;Livraison
                                        gratuite à partir de 89€
                                    </font>
              </h5>
              <img class="img-fluid o_we_custom_image mr-4 mt-2" src="/pepindepomme_custom_website/static/src/img/home/Plan_x0020_1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" data-original-title="" title="" aria-describedby="tooltip802397" data-original-id="617" data-original-src="/pepindepomme_custom_website/static/src/img/home/Plan_x0020_1.png" data-mimetype="image/png" data-resize-width="94"/>
